creator: Virtuagym Professional
descriptionHtml:
TDF Programming App
This new App gives you the ability to get customized training and diet programs. All programs are designed to your specific and personal needs.
TDF stands for Time Distance Force programming and is backed by a team of highly trained and experienced qualified professionals ensuring you with the best possible personalized training program and diet that will help you to achieve your goals faster.

The built-in online platform gives athletes and coaches easy and user-friendly possibilities to meet and stay remotely in contact with each other. TDF Programming provides an advanced direct 2-way communication for feedback, assessment, evaluation, monitoring and even adjusting programming online in real-time, effectively bridging the distance between athlete and coach.

Now you can stay in touch with your coach, no matter the distance!

TDF Programming App is uniquely developed for the following sporting platforms:
Crossfit programming for beginner, experienced and advanced athletes.
Bodybuild programming for both male and females.
Fitness programming for beginner, experienced and advanced athletes.


TDF Programming App provides the following features:
Personalized training programs
Personalized diet
Online community platform
Keeping track of your results and goals
Be assigned to your own coach/trainer and stay in contact with him/her

PLEASE NOTE: YOU NEED A Gym Punt Uit ACCOUNT TO ACCESS THIS APP. IF YOU'RE A MEMBER GET IT FOR FREE AT YOUR GYM!

Begin your journey to a healthier lifestyle and let Gym Punt Uit help you along the way. Introducing Gym Punt Uit, most comprehensive fitness platform with:

Check class schedules and opening hours
Track your daily fitness activities
Track your weight and other body metrics
Over 2000+ exercises and activities
Clear 3D exercise demonstrations
Preset workouts and the option to create your own
Over 150 badges to earn

Select workouts online and synchronize them with your app to workout at home or in the gym while keeping track of your progress. From strength to weight lifting, this app acts as your own personal trainer guiding and giving you the motivation you need.
